Example
Get the language of your browser:

Copy
let x = "Language of the browser: " + navigator.language;

Description
The language property returns the language version of the browser.

This property is read-only.

Browser Compatibility
Chrome.png	Node.png	Firefox.png	Safari.png	Edge.png	Opera.png
language	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes
Syntax
Copy
navigator.language
Return Value
A String, representing the language version of the browser.

Examples of valid language codes are: "en", "en-US", "de", "fr", etc.
